


Implicit waits:

     It's a global wait.Once you declared you don't need to declare again
     It's going to wait until the web element is found.

       driver.manage().timeouts().implicitlyWait(Duration.ofSeconds(20));---waits until 20 sec


       Explicit Waits;
      Wait until certain condition is fullfiled

       This condition would be :
       Element is
       .clickble
       .visible
       .hasText etc.

       wait.until.Elementisvisible